{"tid":2489784,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"怕貓狗 怕動物 但有養寵物嘅朋友逼我鍾意","createTime":"2021-04-15T07:16:46.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-15T07:47:37.000Z","uid":358152,"like":4,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"afe478bbe9e45b8529321de58c9dcdeba2c2048c","tid":2489784,"uid":358152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T07:16:46.000Z","msg":"由細到大都怕貓狗兔金魚<br />\n基本上動物都驚。<br />\n可能係因為有攻擊性（咬/抓），<br />\n又唔知佢想點，<br />\n所以都係避得就避。<br />\n<br />\n我驚又唔代表我係虐待動物嘅人，<br />\n因為我連行近啲都唔想，<br />\n亦都唔覺得自己需要克服，<br />\n因為我呢世都唔會養，<br />\n唔係我冇愛心，<br />\n但我嘅愛心係可以俾小朋友，<br />\n愛心俾啲有需要又溝通到嘅人。<br />\n<br />\n但有養貓狗嘅朋友，<br />\n成日都話：<br />\n「我隻貓唔係咁㗎」<br />\n「我隻狗好乖好蠢㗎」<br />\n「你試下同佢玩 就會鍾意佢㗎喇」<br />\n<br />\n點解要逼我鍾意？ <br />\n你覺得佢係你家人朋友，<br />\n我覺得佢同蟾蛇蜘蛛一樣 (有人養蟾蛇蜘蛛）<br />\n我就係驚，就係唔想鍾意，就係唔覺得佢係朋友家人，<br />\n係咪咁都唔得/ 冇愛心？"},{"pid":"0fed70f986ef85b2f32f246690936de41554e06c","tid":2489784,"uid":127033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T07:20:23.000Z","msg":"不正常人類研究中心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d340e2bbfd18e37fd77dc3e5d0fa10307faa17f7","tid":2489784,"uid":124832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T07:25:56.000Z","msg":"經常有養狗人士講 我隻狗唔咬人嫁<br />\n你隻狗唔咬主人 唔代表唔咬其他人<br />\n<br />\n好似狗咁 突然既受驚 可能會令佢失控"},{"pid":"825499cfdaf03264a074b7a1da7b63fe086409c9","tid":2489784,"uid":57488,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T07:28:56.000Z","msg":"想知如果有百厭細路整到你會點"},{"pid":"51efd14b1414bc417045329c265fab07cccedd2f","tid":2489784,"uid":42350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"825499cfdaf03264a074b7a1da7b63fe086409c9","tid":2489784,"uid":57488,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T07:28:56.000Z","msg":"想知如果有百厭細路整到你會點"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T07:30:02.000Z","msg":"掉落街？<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"402144e87e48f0cb21f35b5722327fff65fa9e86","tid":2489784,"uid":12426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"825499cfdaf03264a074b7a1da7b63fe086409c9","tid":2489784,"uid":57488,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T07:28:56.000Z","msg":"想知如果有百厭細路整到你會點"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T07:35:11.000Z","msg":"溝通唔走就走開<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09799e552afc9bc9886c885685b63c2828ce7211","tid":2489784,"uid":358152,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"825499cfdaf03264a074b7a1da7b63fe086409c9","tid":2489784,"uid":57488,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T07:28:56.000Z","msg":"想知如果有百厭細路整到你會點"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T07:36:20.000Z","msg":"佢整到我，但佢唔會整到我流血/ 咬我 / 流口水落我到，我可以問佢：做乜野點解要咁做，佢可以溝通到。<br />\n<br />\n就算真係純粹百厭咪叫返佢老豆老母教佢，而家我唔會再見到佢。<br />\n<br />\n即係我講緊貓狗都好，我避得就避，係唔鍾意，係個人感受，係個人選擇唔接觸，但亦唔會傷害。 逼人鍾意先係自私"},{"pid":"e7caf6a899f2baba9591c04f1158867af2bc3709","tid":2489784,"uid":30510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T07:36:46.000Z","msg":"咁咪絕交囉"},{"pid":"24de79a325d40bc82ff4ea732c75aceb1463f3b9","tid":2489784,"uid":57488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T07:37:25.000Z","msg":"咁我都同意呢啲野真係無得迫嘅"},{"pid":"e6a0562f73bb04ff140ed040289ebab8400ff626","tid":2489784,"uid":65142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T07:38:02.000Z","msg":"我明<br />\n我都係驚超動物既人<br />\n成日有啲人話你呢啲女人扮哂野 搏同情<br />\n呢個時候我會攞193做例子 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢牛高馬大咁都驚啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac0effb05e8bfc71a4da930ce7e55fe87cf97c6b","tid":2489784,"uid":70888,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T07:40:18.000Z","msg":"逼咩撚野鍾意<br />\n佢咁鍾意 叫佢食埋動物啲屎尿撈飯啦"},{"pid":"a1298e71f61b3faea861887c2a5cf0adb4d2821c","tid":2489784,"uid":384666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T07:44:47.000Z","msg":"你堆朋友問題有問題啫<br />\n唔鐘意小動物冇問題架 <br />\n有啲人係鐘意迫人跟佢個套，唔需要在意同理會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9a680076508e4dc930b14ea160585950ed3a7c8","tid":2489784,"uid":10788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T07:47:37.000Z","msg":"小朋友溝通到？你都on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最憎小朋友最鍾意動物 不過個人喜好 關人撚事"}]}